# Why: Documenso's monorepo build runs `npm run typecheck && react-router build`
#      inside `apps/remix`. The combined tsc + react-router pass exhausts Node's
#      default ~1GB v8 heap on a vanilla Coolify build, OOMing with:
#
#        FATAL ERROR: Ineffective mark-compacts near heap limit
#        Allocation failed - JavaScript heap out of memory
#
#      Setting NODE_OPTIONS=--max-old-space-size=4096 before the turbo build
#      gives Node 4GB of heap, which is enough for the full Documenso build.
#
# Why-not-additive: The setting must be in the Docker build context (specifically
#      the `installer` stage where `RUN turbo run build` executes). It cannot
#      be supplied via Coolify env vars because Documenso's Dockerfile does not
#      declare NODE_OPTIONS as an ARG, and only declared ARGs flow into the
#      build environment from Coolify.
#
# Upstream-merge-fragility: LOW. The added 3 lines (1 ENV + 2 comment) live
#      between two existing instructions that don't change often. Even if
#      upstream restructures the installer stage, re-anchoring is mechanical
#      (find `RUN turbo run build`, ensure NODE_OPTIONS is set above it).
#
# Production memory requirement: the build container needs ≥4GB available RAM
#      during deploys. If your VPS is < 4GB total, lower this value to 2048 or
#      add swap. With 4GB+ free this builds in ~10 min; under-resourced VPSes
#      will OOM-kill at the kernel level (different signature: silent SIGKILL
#      instead of v8's "heap out of memory" message).
#
# Status: APPLIED 2026-04-30 (after first Coolify deploy attempt OOMed at
#         default 1GB heap during the @documenso/remix typecheck step).

diff --git a/docker/Dockerfile b/docker/Dockerfile
index 47304ba8d..4208f786b 100644
--- a/docker/Dockerfile
+++ b/docker/Dockerfile
@@ -81,6 +81,10 @@ COPY turbo.json turbo.json

 RUN npm install -g "turbo@^1.9.3"

+# MODIFIED for BizRethink: raise Node heap during build (default 1GB is too small
+# for monorepo tsc + react-router build). See overlays/003.
+ENV NODE_OPTIONS="--max-old-space-size=4096"
+
 RUN turbo run build --filter=@documenso/remix...

 ###########################
